<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg">
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>KOSIQ - Investor Presentation 2026</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
*,*::before,*::after{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
:root{--blue:#26acf7;--dark:#231f20;--gray:#6b7280;--light-gray:#f3f4f6;--white:#ffffff;--green:#10b981;--red:#ef4444;--amber:#f59e0b}
html,body{height:100%;overflow:hidden;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;background:#000;color:var(--dark)}
.logo{font-weight:900;letter-spacing:-1px}
.logo .kos{color:var(--dark)}.logo .iq{color:var(--blue)}
.deck{position:relative;width:100%;height:100%}
.slide{position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;opacity:0;pointer-events:none;transition:opacity .5s ease,transform .5s ease;transform:scale(.97);background:var(--white)}
.slide.active{opacity:1;pointer-events:auto;transform:scale(1);z-index:2}
.slide-inner{width:min(1120px,90%);max-height:90%;overflow-y:auto}
h1{font-size:clamp(28px,4vw,56px);font-weight:800;line-height:1.1;color:var(--dark);margin-bottom:.4em}
h2{font-size:clamp(22px,3vw,40px);font-weight:700;line-height:1.2;color:var(--dark);margin-bottom:.6em}
h3{font-size:clamp(16px,1.8vw,24px);font-weight:600;color:var(--dark);margin-bottom:.4em}
p,.desc{font-size:clamp(13px,1.4vw,18px);color:var(--gray);line-height:1.6}
.subtitle{font-size:clamp(16px,2vw,24px);color:var(--gray);font-weight:400;margin-bottom:.3em}
.tag{display:inline-block;background:var(--blue);color:#fff;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;padding:6px 16px;border-radius:20px;margin-top:12px}
.accent{color:var(--blue)}
.grid2{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:32px}
.grid3{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr;gap:24px}
.grid4{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;gap:20px}
.card{background:var(--light-gray);border-radius:16px;padding:24px}
.card h3{margin-bottom:8px}
.card p{font-size:14px}
.card-blue{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--blue),#1a8fd4);color:#fff}
.card-blue h3,.card-blue p{color:#fff}
.stat{text-align:center;padding:20px}
.stat .num{font-size:clamp(28px,3.5vw,48px);font-weight:800;color:var(--blue);line-height:1}
.stat .label{font-size:14px;color:var(--gray);margin-top:6px}
ul{list-style:none;padding:0}
ul li{position:relative;padding-left:20px;margin-bottom:10px;font-size:clamp(13px,1.3vw,17px);color:#374151;line-height:1.5}
ul li::before{content:'';position:absolute;left:0;top:8px;width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--blue)}
.steps{display:flex;gap:16px;margin-top:20px}
.step{flex:1;text-align:center;padding:20px 12px;background:var(--light-gray);border-radius:16px;position:relative}
.step .step-num{width:36px;height:36px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--blue);color:#fff;font-weight:700;font-size:16px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin:0 auto 10px}
.step h3{font-size:15px;margin-bottom:6px}
.step p{font-size:13px;color:var(--gray)}
.step+.step::before{content:'';position:absolute;left:-20px;top:50%;width:24px;height:2px;background:#d1d5db}
table{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-size:clamp(11px,1.1vw,14px);margin-top:16px}
th{background:var(--dark);color:#fff;padding:10px 12px;text-align:left;font-weight:600}
td{padding:10px 12px;border-bottom:1px solid #e5e7eb}
tr:nth-child(even) td{background:#f9fafb}
.check{color:var(--green);font-weight:700}.cross{color:#d1d5db;font-weight:700}.partial{color:var(--amber);font-weight:700}
.quote{font-size:clamp(18px,2.2vw,28px);font-style:italic;color:var(--dark);line-height:1.5;border-left:4px solid var(--blue);padding-left:24px;margin:24px 0}
.quote-author{font-size:16px;color:var(--gray);margin-top:8px;font-style:normal;font-weight:600}
.bar{height:8px;border-radius:4px;background:#e5e7eb;margin-top:6px;margin-bottom:16px;overflow:hidden}
.bar-fill{height:100%;border-radius:4px;background:var(--blue)}
.tier{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:16px;padding:16px 20px;background:var(--light-gray);border-radius:12px;margin-bottom:12px}
.tier-price{font-size:28px;font-weight:800;color:var(--blue);white-space:nowrap}
.tier-name{font-weight:700;font-size:16px;color:var(--dark)}
.tier-desc{font-size:13px;color:var(--gray)}
.fund-row{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;margin-bottom:14px}
.fund-pct{font-size:28px;font-weight:800;color:var(--blue);width:70px;text-align:right}
.fund-label{font-weight:600;font-size:16px}
.fund-desc{font-size:13px;color:var(--gray)}
.milestone{display:inline-block;background:var(--light-gray);border-radius:10px;padding:12px 20px;margin:6px;font-weight:600;font-size:15px}
.controls{position:fixed;bottom:20px;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;z-index:100}
.dot{width:10px;height:10px;border-radius:50%;background:rgba(255,255,255,.3);cursor:pointer;transition:all .2s;border:none;padding:0}
.dot.active{background:var(--blue);transform:scale(1.3)}
.slide-counter{position:fixed;bottom:22px;right:24px;font-size:13px;color:rgba(0,0,0,.35);font-weight:500;z-index:100}
.fs-btn{position:fixed;bottom:20px;left:24px;background:rgba(0,0,0,.06);border:none;border-radius:8px;padding:6px 12px;cursor:pointer;font-size:12px;color:var(--gray);font-family:'Inter';z-index:100}
.fs-btn:hover{background:rgba(0,0,0,.1)}
.title-slide{background:linear-gradient(160deg,#fff 60%,#e8f6fe 100%)}
.title-slide .slide-inner{text-align:center}
.title-logo{font-size:clamp(56px,8vw,96px);font-weight:900;letter-spacing:-3px;margin-bottom:16px}
.contact-slide{background:linear-gradient(160deg,#fff 40%,#e8f6fe 100%)}
.contact-slide .slide-inner{text-align:center}
.contact-item{font-size:18px;color:var(--gray);margin:10px 0}
.contact-item a{color:var(--blue);text-decoration:none;font-weight:500}
.section-tag{font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:var(--blue);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:12px}
.demo-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:16px;margin-top:16px}
.demo-card{background:var(--light-gray);border-radius:12px;padding:32px 24px;text-align:center;border:2px solid #e5e7eb}
.demo-card h3{color:var(--dark);font-size:16px}
.demo-card p{font-size:13px;color:var(--gray);margin-top:4px}
.phase{padding:20px 24px;border-left:3px solid var(--blue);margin-bottom:16px;background:var(--light-gray);border-radius:0 12px 12px 0}
.phase h3{font-size:16px;margin-bottom:4px}
.phase p{font-size:14px;color:var(--gray)}
.proj-row{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:14px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #e5e7eb}
.proj-row:last-child{border:none}
.proj-label{font-weight:600;font-size:16px}
.proj-val{font-size:24px;font-weight:800;color:var(--blue)}
@media print{
.controls,.slide-counter,.fs-btn{display:none!important}
.slide{position:relative!important;opacity:1!important;transform:none!important;pointer-events:auto!important;page-break-after:always;break-after:page;height:100vh;z-index:auto!important}
body{overflow:visible}
.deck{position:static}
}
@media(max-width:768px){
.grid2,.grid3,.grid4{grid-template-columns:1fr}
.steps{flex-direction:column}
.step+.step::before{display:none}
table{font-size:11px}
th,td{padding:6px 8px}
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="deck" id="deck">

<!-- Slide 1: Title -->
<div class="slide title-slide active" data-slide="0">
<div class="slide-inner">
<div class="title-logo"><span class="kos">KOS</span><span class="iq" style="color:var(--blue)">IQ</span></div>
<p class="subtitle">AI-Powered Medical Economics Intelligence</p>
<p style="color:#9ca3af;font-size:16px;margin-top:24px">Investor Presentation &nbsp;|&nbsp; 2026</p>
</div>
</div>

<!-- Slide 2: The Problem -->
<div class="slide" data-slide="1">
<div class="slide-inner">
<p class="section-tag">The Problem</p>
<h2>Managed Care Analytics Are Broken</h2>
<div class="grid2">
<div>
<ul>
<li>Practices manage thousands of patients across multiple payers with no unified view</li>
<li>Current tools (legacy platforms) are outdated, manual, and purely retrospective</li>
<li>Zero AI, zero predictive analytics, zero actionable recommendations</li>
<li>CMOs spend hours manually reviewing reports to identify at-risk patients</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div>
<div class="card card-blue">
<h3>$53B+ Market</h3>
<p>Healthcare analytics growing at 21%+ CAGR &mdash; dominated by legacy tools ripe for disruption</p>
</div>
<div class="card" style="margin-top:16px">
<h3>The Reality</h3>
<p>Retrospective data tells you what happened. It does nothing to prevent the next hospitalization, the next cost spike, the next missed diagnosis.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<!-- Slide 3: The Solution -->
<div class="slide" data-slide="2">
<div class="slide-inner">
<p class="section-tag">The Solution</p>
<h2><span class="logo"><span class="kos">KOS</span><span class="iq">IQ</span></span>: AI Medical Economics Platform</h2>
<p class="desc" style="max-width:700px;margin-bottom:28px">Ingest claims data from any payer. AI cleans and normalizes. Deliver actionable intelligence that saves lives and reduces costs.</p>
<div class="grid3">
<div class="card">
<h3 class="accent">Predictive Analytics</h3>
<p>30/60/90-day hospitalization risk, LACE scoring, cost forecasting powered by AI models</p>
</div>
<div class="card">
<h3 class="accent">AI Recommendations</h3>
<p>Monthly prioritized action reports with financial impact estimates for every patient cohort</p>
</div>
<div class="card">
<h3 class="accent">Clinical Alert Programs</h3>
<p>8 physician-designed protocols identifying high-risk patients before adverse events occur</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<!-- Slide 4: Product -->
<div class="slide" data-slide="3">
<div class="slide-inner">
<p class="section-tag">The Product</p>
<h2>Built for How CMOs Actually Work</h2>
<div class="demo-grid">
<div class="demo-card">
<h3>Dashboard Action Center</h3>
<p>Unified view of all payer populations with real-time KPIs and alerts</p>
</div>
<div class="demo-card">
<h3>Predictive Analytics</h3>
<p>ML-powered risk stratification across hospitalization, cost, and quality metrics</p>
</div>
<div class="demo-card">
<h3>AI Recommendations</h3>
<p>Automated monthly reports with prioritized clinical and financial actions</p>
</div>
<div class="demo-card">
<h3>AI Chat Assistant</h3>
<p>Natural language queries: "Show me diabetic patients with rising HbA1c and no PCP visit in 90 days"</p>
</div>
</div>
<p style="text-align:center;margin-top:20px"><span class="tag">Live Demo: kosiq.ai</span></p>
</div>
</div>

<!-- Slide 5: How It Works -->
<div class="slide" data-slide="4">
<div class="slide-inner">
<p class="section-tag">How It Works</p>
<h2>From Raw Claims to Action in Four Steps</h2>
<div class="steps">
<div class="step">
<div class="step-num">1</div>
<h3>Connect</h3>
<p>Payer claims, eligibility, and pharmacy data from any format</p>
</div>
<div class="step">
<div class="step-num">2</div>
<h3>AI Processing</h3>
<p>Clean, normalize, and enrich data with intelligent mapping</p>
</div>
<div class="step">
<div class="step-num">3</div>
<h3>Intelligence</h3>
<p>Real-time dashboards, predictive models, and recommendations</p>
</div>
<div class="step">
<div class="step-num">4</div>
<h3>Action</h3>
<p>Automated monthly reports with prioritized intervention items</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<!-- Slide 6: Key Features -->
<div class="slide" data-slide="5">
<div class="slide-inner">
<p class="section-tag">Key Features</p>
<h2>Comprehensive Intelligence Suite</h2>
<div class="grid2">
<div>
<ul>
<li><strong>20+ Analytics Dashboards</strong> &mdash; Membership, pharmacy, hospitalization, claims, finance, referrals, billing/MRA</li>
<li><strong>Predictive Analytics</strong> &mdash; 30/60/90-day hospitalization risk, LACE scoring, cost forecasting</li>
<li><strong>AI Recommendations</strong> &mdash; Monthly reports with prioritized actions and financial impact estimates</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div>
<ul>
<li><strong>AI Chat Assistant</strong> &mdash; Natural language queries on any patient data</li>
<li><strong>8 Clinical Alert Programs</strong> &mdash; SMI, HIV, ESRD, CKD, HbA1c&gt;9, COPD/Asthma, Unengaged, Age-Provider Mismatch</li>
<li><strong>Enterprise-Grade</strong> &mdash; Role-based access, audit logging, session management</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
<p style="margin-top:16px;font-size:14px;color:var(--gray)">All clinical alert programs designed by Dr. JD Suarez from real-world managed care practice.</p>
</div>
</div>

<!-- Slide 7: Competitive Landscape -->
<div class="slide" data-slide="6">
<div class="slide-inner">
<p class="section-tag">Competitive Landscape</p>
<h2>Legacy Tools vs. AI-Native Platform</h2>
<table>
<tr><th>Capability</th><th style="background:var(--blue)">KOSIQ</th><th>Legacy Platforms</th><th>eClinicalWorks</th><th>Arcadia</th><th>Innovaccer</th></tr>
<tr><td>AI-Powered Analytics</td><td class="check">Yes</td><td class="cross">No</td><td class="cross">No</td><td class="partial">Limited</td><td class="partial">Limited</td></tr>
<tr><td>Predictive Analytics</td><td class="check">Yes</td><td class="cross">No</td><td class="cross">No</td><td class="partial">Basic</td><td class="partial">Basic</td></tr>
<tr><td>AI Recommendations</td><td class="check">Yes</td><td class="cross">No</td><td class="cross">No</td><td class="cross">No</td><td class="cross">No</td></tr>
<tr><td>Natural Language Chat</td><td class="check">Yes</td><td class="cross">No</td><td class="cross">No</td><td class="cross">No</td><td class="cross">No</td></tr>
<tr><td>Clinical Alert Programs</td><td class="check">8 Protocols</td><td class="cross">No</td><td class="partial">Basic</td><td class="partial">Limited</td><td class="partial">Limited</td></tr>
<tr><td>Modern UI/UX</td><td class="check">Yes</td><td class="cross">Dated</td><td class="cross">Dated</td><td class="partial">Moderate</td><td class="check">Yes</td></tr>
<tr><td>Setup Time</td><td class="check">Days</td><td class="cross">Months</td><td class="cross">Months</td><td class="cross">Months</td><td class="cross">Months</td></tr>
<tr><td>Price Point</td><td class="check">Accessible</td><td class="partial">High</td><td class="partial">High</td><td class="cross">Enterprise</td><td class="cross">Enterprise</td></tr>
</table>
</div>
</div>

<!-- Slide 8: Market Opportunity -->
<div class="slide" data-slide="7">
<div class="slide-inner">
<p class="section-tag">Market Opportunity</p>
<h2>Massive and Growing Addressable Market</h2>
<div class="grid2">
<div>
<div class="stat"><div class="num">$59.7B</div><div class="label">US Healthcare Analytics Market by 2030</div></div>
<div class="bar"><div class="bar-fill" style="width:33%"></div></div>
<p style="font-size:13px;color:var(--gray);text-align:center">$19.65B (2025) at 24.9% CAGR</p>
<div class="stat" style="margin-top:20px"><div class="num">$456.6B</div><div class="label">Medicare Advantage Market | 33M+ Enrollees</div></div>
</div>
<div>
<div class="card" style="margin-bottom:16px">
<h3>TAM</h3>
<p>~3,000 large managed care groups (20K+ patients) in the US</p>
</div>
<div class="card" style="margin-bottom:16px">
<h3>SAM</h3>
<p>~1,500 groups with 40,000+ members (our sweet spot)</p>
</div>
<div class="card card-blue">
<h3>SOM &mdash; Year 3</h3>
<p>25 groups in Year 3 = <strong>$15M+ ARR</strong></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<!-- Slide 9: Market Validation -->
<div class="slide" data-slide="8">
<div class="slide-inner">
<p class="section-tag">Market Validation</p>
<h2>Cozeva Proves the Market &mdash; KOSIQ Accelerates It</h2>
<div class="grid2" style="margin-top:20px">
<div>
<h3 style="margin-bottom:16px">Cozeva: 14 Years to $50-100M</h3>
<div style="display:flex;gap:12px;margin-bottom:14px">
<div style="min-width:55px;text-align:center;padding:6px;background:var(--light-gray);border-radius:8px;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;color:var(--gray)">2012</div>
<div><p style="font-size:13px"><strong>Founded</strong> — Quality measurement tools for CA health plans. No AI. No predictive analytics. Bootstrapped.</p></div>
</div>
<div style="display:flex;gap:12px;margin-bottom:14px">
<div style="min-width:55px;text-align:center;padding:6px;background:var(--light-gray);border-radius:8px;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;color:var(--gray)">2016</div>
<div><p style="font-size:13px"><strong>Product-market fit</strong> — First major clients. 15 quality awards. ~$5M estimated revenue.</p></div>
</div>
<div style="display:flex;gap:12px;margin-bottom:14px">
<div style="min-width:55px;text-align:center;padding:6px;background:var(--light-gray);border-radius:8px;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;color:var(--gray)">2019</div>
<div><p style="font-size:13px"><strong>Scale</strong> — 50+ quality awards. Multi-state expansion. ~$20M estimated revenue.</p></div>
</div>
<div style="display:flex;gap:12px;margin-bottom:14px">
<div style="min-width:55px;text-align:center;padding:6px;background:var(--light-gray);border-radius:8px;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;color:var(--gray)">2026</div>
<div><p style="font-size:13px"><strong>Market leader</strong> — 84 clients, 25M lives, 30 states, Best in KLAS. $50-100M revenue. ~500 employees.</p></div>
</div>
<div class="card" style="background:#fff;border:1px solid #e5e7eb;padding:14px;margin-top:8px">
<p style="font-size:13px;color:var(--gray)"><strong style="color:var(--dark)">Key insight:</strong> Cozeva built a $50-100M business with no AI, no predictive analytics, no chat interface, and no venture funding. Pure analytics reporting.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<h3 style="margin-bottom:16px">KOSIQ: Built for Today's Market</h3>
<div class="card" style="margin-bottom:12px;padding:16px;border-left:4px solid var(--blue)">
<p style="font-size:14px"><strong style="color:var(--blue)">5x Larger Market</strong></p>
<p style="font-size:13px;color:var(--gray)">Healthcare analytics was $10B in 2012. It's $53B+ today and growing 21% CAGR. The opportunity is fundamentally different.</p>
</div>
<div class="card" style="margin-bottom:12px;padding:16px;border-left:4px solid var(--green)">
<p style="font-size:14px"><strong style="color:var(--green)">AI-Native from Day One</strong></p>
<p style="font-size:13px;color:var(--gray)">Cozeva retrofitted AI years later. KOSIQ is built on it &mdash; predictive models, natural language chat, automated recommendations. What took them 10 years to add, we ship at launch.</p>
</div>
<div class="card" style="margin-bottom:12px;padding:16px;border-left:4px solid #8b5cf6">
<p style="font-size:14px"><strong style="color:#8b5cf6">Capital-Accelerated Growth</strong></p>
<p style="font-size:13px;color:var(--gray)">Cozeva bootstrapped to $50-100M over 14 years. With $2-5M in seed funding, a built-in clinical network, and AI-powered sales enablement, KOSIQ targets $15M+ ARR in 3 years.</p>
</div>
<div class="card" style="margin-bottom:12px;padding:16px;border-left:4px solid var(--amber)">
<p style="font-size:14px"><strong style="color:var(--amber)">Aggressive Pricing</strong></p>
<p style="font-size:13px;color:var(--gray)">Cozeva charges an estimated $1-3 PMPM for their full platform. KOSIQ enters at $0.50-$2.24 PMPM &mdash; same value-based analytics plus AI, at a fraction of the cost.</p>
</div>
<div style="background:var(--light-gray);border-radius:12px;padding:16px;text-align:center;margin-top:8px">
<p style="font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:var(--dark)">Cozeva validated the market.</p>
<p style="font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:var(--blue)">KOSIQ captures it faster, smarter, and cheaper.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<!-- Slide 10: Business Model -->
<div class="slide" data-slide="9">
<div class="slide-inner">
<p class="section-tag">Business Model</p>
<h2>PMPM Pricing + Full Integration Services</h2>
<div class="grid2">
<div>
<div class="card" style="border-top:4px solid var(--blue);margin-bottom:16px">
<h3 style="color:var(--blue)">Per Member Per Month (PMPM)</h3>
<p style="font-size:14px;margin-bottom:12px">Targeting large managed care groups with 20,000-60,000+ members. Scales with population size.</p>
<div class="tier">
<div><div class="tier-name">60,000+ members</div></div>
<div class="tier-price" style="margin-left:auto">$0.50<span style="font-size:14px;font-weight:400"> PMPM</span></div>
</div>
<div class="tier">
<div><div class="tier-name">20,000 - 60,000 members</div></div>
<div class="tier-price" style="margin-left:auto">$1.25<span style="font-size:14px;font-weight:400"> PMPM</span></div>
</div>
<div class="tier">
<div><div class="tier-name">Under 20,000 members</div></div>
<div class="tier-price" style="margin-left:auto">$2.24<span style="font-size:14px;font-weight:400"> PMPM</span></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="card" style="border-top:4px solid var(--green)">
<h3 style="color:var(--green)">Full Integration Services</h3>
<p style="font-size:14px;margin-bottom:8px">Custom EHR integrations, real-time data feeds, dedicated support, white-glove onboarding.</p>
<div class="tier">
<div><div class="tier-name">Starting at</div></div>
<div class="tier-price" style="margin-left:auto">$10K+<span style="font-size:14px;font-weight:400">/mo</span></div>
</div>
