<p style="font-size:13px;color:var(--gray)">$175B+ revenue &bull; 40M+ members &bull; ~$70B market cap<br>Anthem Blue Cross, BCBS affiliates across 14 states<br>Medicare, Medicaid, Commercial &mdash; all lines of business</p>
