<p style="font-size:13px;color:var(--gray)">If Elevance mandates KOSIQ for even 10% of their contracted provider groups:<br><br><strong>4M members x $1 PMPM = $4M/mo = $48M ARR</strong><br><br>From a single partnership. That alone puts us at Cozeva's level.</p>
