<p style="font-size:13px;color:var(--gray)">Payers lose money on avoidable hospitalizations. KOSIQ's predictive analytics identify at-risk patients BEFORE they end up in the ER. For Elevance, a 5% reduction in avoidable admits across 4M members saves them <strong>$200M+ annually</strong>. KOSIQ pays for itself 50x over.</p>
