<p style="font-weight:700;color:var(--dark);font-size:13px;margin-bottom:6px">How We Got These Numbers</p>
<table style="width:100%;font-size:12px;border-collapse:collapse">
<tr style="border-bottom:1px solid #e5e7eb"><td style="padding:3px 0"><strong>Year 1:</strong> 5 groups x 20K avg members = 100K members</td><td style="text-align:right">100K x $1.25 PMPM x 12 = <strong>$1.5M</strong></td></tr>
<tr style="border-bottom:1px solid #e5e7eb"><td style="padding:3px 0"><strong>Year 2:</strong> 12 groups x 33K avg members = 400K members</td><td style="text-align:right">400K x $1.25 PMPM x 12 = <strong>$6M</strong></td></tr>
<tr><td style="padding:3px 0"><strong>Year 3:</strong> 25 groups x 40K avg members = 1M members</td><td style="text-align:right">1M x $1.25 PMPM x 12 = <strong>$15M</strong></td></tr>
</table>
<p style="margin-top:8px;font-size:11px">Avg PMPM of $1.25 is blended across tiers ($0.50-$2.24). Integration revenue assumes ~40-60% of customers opt for full integration services.</p>
